Package org.apache.juddi.api.impl

This package contains the web service implementation classes of all jUDDI services

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UDDIServiceCounterMBean  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthenticatedService
    Although this class is abstract, it provides token validation
    InquiryHelper
    Co Used to factor out inquiry functionality as it is used in more than one spot.
    JUDDIApiImpl
    Implements the jUDDI API service.
    PublicationHelper
    Used to factor out publication functionality that is used in more than one spot.
    ServiceCounterLifecycleResource  
    UDDICustodyTransferImpl
    This implements the UDDI v3 Custody Transfer API web service
    UDDIInquiryImpl
    This implements the UDDI v3 Inquiry API web service
    UDDIPublicationImpl
    This class implements the UDDI Publication Service
    UDDIReplicationImpl
    UDDI Replication defines four APIs.
    UDDISecurityImpl
    This class implements the UDDI Security Service and basically handles all authentication requests for jUDDI.
    UDDIServiceCounter
    This class provides MBean functionality that offers metrics on UDDI service method invocations and various management functions (documented by Alex O'Ree)
    UDDISubscriptionImpl
    This is jUDDI's implementation of the UDDIv3 Subscription API
    UDDISubscriptionListenerImpl
    This class implements the UDDI v3 Subscription Listener API (server side) for jUDDI.
    UDDIv2InquiryImpl
    UDDI v2 Implementation for the Inquiry service.
    UDDIv2PublishImpl
    UDDI v2 Implementation for the Publish service.
    UDDIValueSetCachingImpl  
    UDDIValueSetValidationImpl
    Implementation the UDDI v3 spec for Value Set Validation This is basically used to validate Keyed Reference value sets and offers validation via jUDDI's VSV extensibility framework.

    To use this, define a tModel containing the following
    XRegisterHelper
    Used to factor out inquiry functionality as it is used in more than one spot.
